caller_intent: Inform the caller about next steps for a homeowner's policy, including an exclusion form for a shed and requesting proof of roof replacement.
resolution_steps: Sent an exclusion form via email using CongaSign for electronic signature.
Requested proof of roof replacement (paid receipt/invoice) and sent a separate email for that purpose.
Offered in-person assistance at the office if electronic methods are not preferred.
Provided office contact number for follow-up questions.
summary: Jamie Flippin from Alliance Insurance left a voicemail informing Daniel about an exclusion form for a shed and requesting proof of roof replacement. She provided electronic and in-person options for completing paperwork, sent two emails with instructions, and shared her office contact number for further assistance.
